  <div class="docs-callout">
    <div>
      <p><strong>Set hard limits before generating your key.</strong></p>
      <p>
        OpenAI <code>Settings → Billing → Usage limits</code>. For this POC: <strong>Soft $2/mo</strong> + <strong>Hard $5/mo</strong>. The API will return errors past the hard limit. $5 covers ~100 full-repo re-indexes on a 3 k-file project.
      </p>
